<!-- RESULTS -->
<section class="results-section" id="proof">
  <div class="section-wrap">
    <div class="section-label">Experiment Results</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">We tested it. <em>Ecosorb wins.</em></h2>
    <p class="section-lead">Using controlled mason jar tests with a hygrometer and moisture meter, we compared Ecosorb against silica gel and bentonite clay over 9+ hours.</p>
    <div class="result-hero-card">
      <div class="result-big-num">11%</div>
      <div class="result-hero-text">
        <strong>Best moisture reading after 9 hours — Ecosorb (Kraft packaging)</strong>
        <p>Outperformed silica gel, bentonite clay, and our own Tyvek-packaged variant. Lower is better: silica gel reached 14.5% at the same timepoint.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="results-grid">
      <div class="result-card">
        <h3>Head-to-head vs. silica gel</h3>
        <p>In a 72-hour test, our 70/30 Ecosorb blend outperformed silica gel at the 2-hour mark and remained competitive throughout. The Kraft-packaged version showed the strongest sustained performance.</p>
        <div class="result-highlight">✓ Best performer at every measured interval</div>
      </div>
      <div class="result-card">
        <h3>Expert-validated formulation</h3>
        <p>Dr. Aruna Turaga, PhD in Analytical Chemistry from the Indian Institute of Science with six years managing an analytical lab in Seattle, reviewed our methodology and findings.</p>
        <div class="result-highlight">✓ Validated by a credentialed chemistry expert</div>
      </div>
      <div class="result-card">
        <h3>Packaging matters</h3>
        <p>We tested two packaging types — Tyvek and Kraft paper. Kraft consistently outperformed, confirming material selection is as important as the desiccant blend itself.</p>
        <div class="result-highlight">✓ Kraft selected as our production standard</div>
      </div>
      <div class="result-card">
        <h3>Odor control advantage</h3>
        <p>The activated carbon component gives Ecosorb an odor-absorption capability that silica gel simply doesn't have — a meaningful differentiator for footwear and food applications.</p>
        <div class="result-highlight">✓ Absorbs moisture and eliminates odors simultaneously</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

